description:
Gary Numan Cars (Extended Mix). Well, this track changed everything and my life. Gary Numan more or less sold me with this track Cars. I love it, I love it, I love it. Gary's 2nd number 1 chart topping single here in the UK.

Again, this track has had the Pure Salvation Extended Mix treatment.

Enjoy.
